{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Combining the global scale of civilization games with the urgency of real-time strategy. This could be the largest RTS ever made!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Manage the production of men and weapons in your cities to create a relentless flow of soldiers marching toward the jaws to war.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Design your own flag; this will determine the visuals of your soldiers. Then watch the world turn into your color, painted by war!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1223150/extras/city_and_woodcut.gif?t=1730020771\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">City Building: Construct and develop your cities to support your war efforts.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Workers: Assign tasks to your workers, who will follow a priority-based queue system.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Resource Management: Set up production chains with a delivery system to ensure a smooth supply of materials.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Army Controls: Command your forces across the map while keeping them well-supplied and fed.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Diverse Military Units: Deploy various unit types, each with its own strengths and weaknesses.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Diplomacy system: Coerce others into joining your cause.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A multiplayer like no other 4X game. Join forces or end up as bitter enemies - the diplomacy is real.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1223150/extras/steam_desc_zoom_anim_delay.gif?t=1730020771\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Technical Facts</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Pricing: 100% free.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Multiplayer: 1-4 player local split-screen, co-op or versus. Xbox controllers are required.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Input options: Mouse only (with scroll), Mouse &amp; Keyboard or Xbox controller.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Localization: All languages, except for English, are machine translated.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play time: A session is about 4 hours. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Big picture mode: No.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Steam deck: No. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Rebindable keys: Keyboard only. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Supported resolutions: Any.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Multiple monitors: Yes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Framerate: 60</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Offline gameplay: Yes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">System requirements: The game is very CPU heavy, it does not matter what graphics card you have. Running smaller maps reduces CPU load. Multiple cores (up to 16) will improve performance.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Engine: MonoGame/C#/OpenGL.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Original release: &quot;Plunder Party&quot; on Xbox360.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Mature content: Cartoon violence, cubes of blood. Still pictures of monsters and a person on fire (same detail level as the storefront images). No gore, no sex/nudity.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Accessibility: No flashing images. No fast tapping, or holding a button. Text size option.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Development team size: 1</p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Victory 25%","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1223150/3239a386410b7157dfe7691883c133c98bb58f74.jpg"},{"name":"Victory 50%","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1223150/b909f35ab1fc27293240607996624f62